Install XEMU on Elementary OS

Page

1 link to

Main page to install XEMU

Install with PPA

Shell

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:mborgerson/xemu  
sudo apt update  
sudo apt install xemu

Optional install extract-xiso Disk utility to conver direcotry game xbox to valid iso ann run in xemu

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

Extract XIso  

Shell

# Clone Repo  
git clone https://github.com/XboxDev/extract-xiso.git  
  
# cd into directory  
cd extract-xiso  
  
# Create working directory  
mkdir build  
cd build  
  
# Build project  
cmake ..  
make  
  
# This commands will be to create a extract-xiso.bin inside this path we can run this commands  
Command for Extract-XISO:  
ISO to XBE  
./extract-xiso ~/DirectoryName/game.iso  
XBE to ISO  
./extract-xiso -c ~/DirectoryName/game/ ~/DirectoryName/game.iso  
  

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

If fails build cmake run

Shell

sudo apt install cmake  
sudo apt install build-essential
